        "## **1. Executive Summary**\n",
        "This project implements an end-to-end quantitative trading and portfolio management framework. The system automates market data ingestion, generates multi-factor technical indicators, and constructs optimized portfolios using **Risk Parity (Inverse Volatility)** methodologies to ensure stable risk-adjusted returns.\n",
